                <li><MdLink href="https://www.saulleiterfoundation.org/color">Saul Leiter's website</MdLink></li>
                <li><MdLink href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:24_man_in_een_telefooncel-4591445.ogv">24 man in een telefooncel</MdLink></li>
                <li><MdLink href="https://www.oldbookillustrations.com/">Old Book Illustrations</MdLink></li>
                <li><MdLink href="https://www.landfallnavigation.com/noaa-nautical-chart-14909-upper-green-bay-jackson-harbor-and-detroit-harbor-detroit-harbor-jackson-harbor-baileys-harbor.html">Map of Death's Door</MdLink></li>
                <li><MdLink href="https://rsms.me/inter/">Inter, This Font</MdLink></li>
                <li><MdLink href="https://github.com/psb1558/Junicode-font">Junicode, <span class="font-serif">This Font</span></MdLink></li>
                <li><MdLink href="wrapmap">Falafel Wraps</MdLink></li>
                <li><MdLink href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:7-Eleven,_Orlando,_Florida,_August_1987.ogv">7-Eleven, Florida, 1987</MdLink></li>
            </ul>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>
